text: Liamine Zéroual ( ALA-LC: al-Yamīn Zarwāl; Berber: Lyamin Ẓerwal; born 3 July 1941) is an Algerian politician. He was the sixth President of Algeria from 31 January 1994 to 27 April 1999.William Maclean, "Algeria ex-leader will not run for top job", Reuters (IOL), 14 January 2009. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Algeria
title: Liamine Zéroual
